<title>UK: Gencor sets Billiton pricing for July 22.</title>
<headline>Gencor sets Billiton pricing for July 22.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>South African mining group Gencor Ltd said on Friday it expects to price shares in its demerged Billiton base metals group on July 22, in London.</p>
<p>The company said in a statement it expected the initial price to be announced next Tuesday, with conditional dealings on the London Stock Exchange starting at 0730 GMT.</p>
<p>It expects Billiton to be admitted to full listings on the London and Johannesburg exchanges on July 28.</p>
